Thus was the work of the person of Cali which identified the corpse of Alfonso Cano
A dactyloscopist of Cali passed to the history as the man who confirmed the death of “Alfonso Cano'.
The work of these civils servant is crucial.
The past November 4th a dactyloscopist of the CTI of Cali passed to the history like the person who confirmed the identity of the supreme leader of Farc: “Alfonso Cano”, by confronting its digital fingerprints.
Of the seven dactyloscopists who work in the local offices of the CTI, this week it was the turn of “disponibilité' of Eliazar González, a man of Puerto Tejada which has worked for 21 years in the legal field of investigation.
At the beginning of its career, González worked in the municipes of Chocó, where much time it had to pass more than five days in the forest to arrive at the place in which corpses qu were to be identified.
The year 2000 it was done transferred to the capital from Valle and after having follow adequate courses, it specialized in dactyloscopy, which is the study of the skin of friction, i.e. the palms and the feet.
During the week of the operation against alias Alfonso Cano one had informed in Eliazar to take with him clothes at least for three days.
Something of very large expected it.
Friday the night it left for Cauca in a helicopter Palmira.
It knew that it was to identify two corpses and that one suspectait that one of them was that of the man who directed the older guérrilla of the world, consequently one required of him to carry the chart with the ten digital fingerprints of Guillermo León Sáenz (its true name).
But when it arrived with the team of investigation towards corpse, it did not recognize it by its physical aspect, because this one was very different from that which he had seen in the media.
It did not have a barb, it was equipped like a peasant with the zone, without glasses and much thinner.
But the prints do not lie.
Accompanied by a magnifying glass galtonienne, ink, a sampler and a lantern, Eliazar compared the digital fingerprints of the corpse with those of the chart.
Its eye did not mislead it not: it was about “Alfonso Cano”.
This same night, the man originating in Puerto Tejada was the person in charge who confirmed to the minister of Defense, Juan Carlos Pinzón that yes, it was the supreme leader of Farc.
In search of the print
For a dactyloscopist of Sijín de Cali the recognition which president Juan Manuel Santos made in Eliazar González, in a press conference for the operation against “Cano”, is very significant.
Many people of do not know our work.
The dactyloscopy is an exact science, without margin of error, which can be crucial in the resolution of crimes.
Except for identifying the corpses, the dactyloscopists support the investigations for the offenses like the flight and the homicide and confirm the identity of the captured people.
When are captured, much delinquents present false identity cards or do not have documents.
We take their digital fingerprints and let us seek them in the database.
The researcher told that in a case of flight it had to remove part of wall of a house, because in this place the robber had supported his hand to make leave a safe full with jewels and money.
“The walls are difficult because they are not adequate surfaces to draw a digital fingerprint from it, but in this case we could obtain the print of all the hand and to identify with the delinquent who had taken part in various flights”, remembers it.
The prints can also draw aside or confirm suspects in cases of homicide.
Recently one found a man died, with drink bottles around him.
By interlude of the investigation one determined that a relative can be suspect crime and indeed a print on the bottle coincided.
Even if that No does not guarantee that he is the assassin, that places it on the scene of the crime.
A dactyloscopist of the CTI explained that one extracts “the digital fingerprints from the objects with chemical or physical reagents”.
When they appear, one uses a sampler or a band to take them.
Subsequently, the prints are sent to Asif, the database of the déclinquents, or with the National Civil Register.
“The problem is that there are still many Colombians without papers”, indicated the expert of the CTI.
He explained why all is not how one shows in the CSI television program.
As all that shines is not gold, very that one touches does not become forcing a print.
It can however be used, if one carries out confrontation necessary.
